      <title>加拿大推出了45亿加元的计划，以帮助关税公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-rolls-out-4-5-billion-program-to-aid-tariff-hit-firms-m7z2uuqe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员周五宣布，加拿大政府将部署65亿加元（45亿美元），以帮助出口商到达加拿大产品的新市场，并帮助公司导航关税战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/canada-rolls-out-4-5-billion-program-to-aid-tariff-hit-firms-m7z2uuqe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普以4亿美元的联邦赠款削减了反犹太主义的奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府表示，将取消4亿美元的联邦赠款和哥伦比亚大学的合同，理由是犹太学生对常春藤联盟学校的民权投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-hits-columbia-with-400-million-in-cuts-over-antisemitism</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:50:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划限制非营利工人的贷款宽恕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-plans-to-restrict-loan-forgiveness-for-non-profit-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统计划签署一项行政命令，该命令将限制政府经营的学生贷款宽恕计划的资格，以针对非营利组织与政府移民政策发生冲突的个人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-plans-to-restrict-loan-forgiveness-for-non-profit-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:48:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
