    <item>
      <title>图斯克说，波兰应该考虑使用核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/polish-premier-tusk-to-boost-army-to-half-a-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克（Donald Tusk）表示，他的国家可能寻求核武器，警告说欧洲可能会在未来几年内与俄罗斯面对战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/polish-premier-tusk-to-boost-army-to-half-a-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 13:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他寄了伊朗领导人信敦促核谈话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）本周写信给伊朗的领导人，敦促该国谈判一项新的核协议，几天后，德黑兰的原子活动激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
